headline: 3 Reasons to Sell WST and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: West Pharmaceutical Services has gotten torched over the last six months - since October 2024, its stock price has dropped 29.3% to $202.47 per share. This was partly driven by its softer quarterly results and may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
